comments: She is super nice! she tries so hard! I think everyone likes her :) She doesn\'t ever return graded things tho...whatever. It\'s a real easy class.
She is a very nice person and works hard to get to know her students. She is disorganized and takes forever to grade assignments. It wasn\'t a difficult class but I enjoyed it and did learn from her.
This woman is very unorganized. She never grades and returns papers on time, but is a nice woman. However, being a professor takes more than that. I didn\'t actually learn anything from her.
